        public static java.lang.String validPart​(java.lang.String name,
                                         java.lang.String price,
                                         java.lang.String stock,
                                         java.lang.String min,
                                         java.lang.String max,
                                         java.lang.String machOrComp,
                                         boolean madeInHouse)
        This method takes the data input in the text fields and validates them. Eg. name has to be a string and cannot be empty, price must be a double, etc.
        Parameters:
        name - name of part
        price - price of part
        stock - stock of part
        min - minimum inventory level
        max - maximum inventory level
        machOrComp - entered data that may either be the machineID or the companyName
        madeInHouse - whether or not the part was made in house
        Returns:
        invalid which is a string including data validation errors
